author: The Critical Drinker
description: She shot to fame playing Hermione in Harry Potter, she was the darling of the indy film industry and well on her way to becoming an A-List starlet. But a dangerous flirtation with political activism and a public feud with JK Rowling effectively derailed her career, and just a few days ago, Emma Watson finally crashed and burned in spectacular fashion.
title: Crash And Burn - The Emma Watson Story
